## Gym — Day List (Train tab)

- 4-day Upper/Lower split: Upper A (PUSH · red), Lower A (QUADS · gold), Upper B (PULL · green), Lower B (HAMS · purple)
- "Pick your day." header
- NEXT UP tile (172dp tall): "NEXT UP" pill, large name, subtitle + exercise count, accent START/Continue button
- Compact tiles for other 3 days (96dp): right-side "→" arrow, last-trained date + exercise count
- Next-up rotation logic: Upper A → Lower A → Upper B → Lower B; advances from most-recently-finished session; defaults to Upper A if never trained; active session day takes priority
- Per-day accent color from hex (toAccentColor())
- Spine strip: vertical rotated word (PUSH / QUADS / PULL / HAMS), accent tinted
- Smooth radial bloom gradient via drawBehind (centered at 92–95% card width, fades to transparent)
- ACTIVE dot on card when a session is in progress for that day
- bounceClick spring animation on all cards

