## Gym — Stats tab

Accessed via the Stats tab inside the Gym screen (alongside Train).

- Totals row: total workouts · exercises logged · total PRs
- 12-week frequency heatmap (activity calendar, one cell per day, shaded by exercise count)
- Volume by muscle group chart (horizontal bars, weekly lb)
- Strength curve: line chart of max weight per session for an exercise (~10 most recent points)
- PR timeline list: recent PRs with date, exercise name, weight, reps

