## Gym — Active Workout (Day Screen)

### Warmup Gate
- 4 warmup items per day (day-specific exercises/stretches)
- Checkbox list — auto-advances when all ticked
- "Skip warmup" button
- Gate disappears on completion, exercise list appears

### Session Management
- Session persists to DB on start (survives app kill / rotation)
- Active session rehydrates on screen re-entry
- Discard workout confirmation dialog (only shown if sets have been logged)
- Session duration tracked from start time

### Exercise List
- Collapsible exercise cards (tap to expand/collapse)
- Previous session "last time" text shown per exercise (e.g. "Last: 30 lb × 10")
- Weight prefill from last session

### Set Logging
- Weight + reps input row per set
- PR badge shown inline on set rows where a PR is detected in real time
- PR detection: compares max weight against all historical sets for that exercise

### Per-Exercise Controls
- Difficulty rater: EASY / MODERATE / HARD / BRUTAL (saved to DB per exercise)
- Note field: freeform text saved per logged exercise
- Exercise swap picker sheet:
  - Session-only swap (this workout only)
  - Persistent swap (saved to ExerciseCustomization, applies to all future sessions)
  - Swap candidates filtered by muscle group from the swap catalog
- Skip exercise

### Rest Timer
- Auto-starts (2:30 default) when a set is logged
- Floating FAB bubble on the Scaffold FAB slot: shows countdown (M:SS), accent-colored while running, grey when paused, green when done
- Tap bubble → RestTimerControlsDialog: Pause / Resume / Reset / Skip
- Timer state persisted in ViewModel (survives screen rotation)

### Session Summary Sheet (end of workout)
- Total volume in lb
- PR count (highlighted if > 0)
- Duration in minutes
- Sets logged, exercises logged, exercises skipped
- Per-exercise highlights: sets · volume · PR badge
- Trophies unlocked section (shows new unlocks earned in this session)
- Mood prompt: Drained 😩 / Off 😕 / Fine 😐 / Good 🙂 / Strong 💪 (tap to select, tap again to deselect)
- Done button — saves mood to MoodEntry table, closes sheet

