## Trophies

- 20 trophies across 3 categories: Firsts · Consistency · Strength
- **Firsts (5):** First Session, First PR, Hit the Wall (brutal rating), Made It Mine (swap used), Full Slate (all target sets hit)
- **Consistency (8):** Five Strong / Double Digits / Quarter Hundred / Halfway / Century (session milestones), Through the Door (first full workout), Showing Up (10 full workouts), Full Week (all 4 days trained)
- **Strength (7):** PR Hunter / On a Roll / Forged Strength (PR milestones), 25lb/30lb Bench Club, 30lb Goblet, Volume King (3000 lb session), Volume Beast (5000 lb session)
- Pure-function evaluator: TrophyEvaluator runs against TrophyStatsSnapshot (no DAO deps — testable in isolation)
- Progress hints for locked trophies (e.g. "7 / 10 PRs")
- 2-column grid layout, section headers per category
- Progress bar header: X / 20 unlocked
- Unlock date shown on earned trophy cards
- New unlocks surfaced in Session Summary Sheet immediately after finishing a workout
- 11 icon types mapped to Material Icons (Spark, Star, Flame, Swap, Check, Stack, Crown, Door, Four, Dumbbell, Bolt)

